data.description: Charming 2+ bed home with a big bonus room/3rd bedroom and separate entrance. Recent upgrades include a new mini-split heat/AC system for comfort, newer roof, windows and kitchen/bath updates. Enjoy privacy in the newly fenced yard front and back, an oversized 2-car garage with a spacious shop/storage area. Conveniently located on a corner lot, ready-to-finish attic w/materials for extra living space! Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
